</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Dis-assembly</category></metadata></prolog><conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody "><section id="GUID-92F3C2B2-01C6-4078-AEA6-4C8E31663AA0" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Before you begin</title><p class="- topic/p ">Go to COLD SDS and disconnect the Service jumper. 
</p></section><section id="GUID-AF146350-9059-4A85-ACB2-B63A6674BC5F" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "> 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Required tools</b> </title><p class="- topic/p ">Protective gloves : Microflex 93-260 gloves 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">New manifolds: 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> - 05Y3 (CAR_PURGE_1_VA) 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">- 05Y2 (CAR_PURGE_2_VA) 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">- 05Y1 (CAR_PURGE_3_VA) 
</p></section><section id="GUID-93C4C16B-FD87-4947-A01B-5568A408F0F2" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "> 
