</p></section><section id="GUID-F5034822-753A-4C8B-A7CD-E44CE7EBD702" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="GUID-F8C9A01E-FCB8-4137-8EAE-23BB68BA0B22" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-279C20BD-3317-458C-92CC-E22575617E6D-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-279C20BD-3317-458C-92CC-E22575617E6D-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> 
